g.text: 1. Post Questions – Users can post questions, add topics/tags.
2. Voting System – Users can upvote or downvote questions and answers; ranking is based on total votes.
6. Feed & Recommendations – Personalized home feed based on followed users, topics, and trending content.
7. Search and Filtering – Full-text search across questions, answers, and topics; filter by tags, recency, or popularity.
8. Notifications – Users get notified for new answers, comments, votes, and when followed users post new content.
